          "reviewBody": "Most terrible school i attended in my younger days grade 2 3 4. This was the most traumatizing period of my life..the teachers were extremely toxic and abusive. I remember once i forgot to bring homework..she removed my dress and made me stand in a dustbin with only shirt on for half a day while she used to paint her nails in class...\nI was a good student who used to get good grades and imagine if i was earpulled, beaten on head, punched and what not, what would have the other not so well performing kids gone through with these monstrous teachers...\ni can never forget that trauma these toxic behaviors induced on me growing up with fear...i m surprised this school hasnt been shut down yet..i am sure my other fellow classmates had similar horror stories to share of extreme abuse and toxicity...i will never forget the treatment meted out to me here and would not wish this on any other kid. Please don't send your kids to this school...they don't have an ounce of sensitivity needed to handle gentle minds...shame on their convent culture....",
